Beauty 

Beauty is everywhere, sometimes in the dark
sometimes in the light.
But it's everywhere we go.
We just have to look for it.
It's like a book, how will you know it's a 
good book without reading it?
So sometimes just take some time to look deeper into things.
It's like a flight.
When it's day it's not beautiful, but when dark, lights shimer
like stars from below. 
There's beauty in people, places, normal day items.
You just have to look for it.
And when you find it, your eyes will thank you.